WEBVTT

29:06.390 --> 29:09.070 line:80%
Have you always regretted
having no chance to release a lantern?

29:09.070 --> 29:10.270 line:80%
I'll make it up to you.

29:10.520 --> 29:12.070 line:80%
Shall we write both our names on it?

29:12.070 --> 29:13.550 line:80%
You are disgusting.

29:14.310 --> 29:16.570 line:80%
I'm speaking from the bottom of my heart.
